caption:
🌅✨ “Chasing golden hour views.”
Lena, radiant and carefree in a breezy crop top and denim shorts, stands on a cliff overlooking Ischia’s turquoise sea. With her DSLR in hand, she captures every breathtaking moment while her travel buddy Marco frames the scene from the background. Waves, peaks, and golden sunlight create the perfect cinematic vibe. 📸🌊
